 er til stede og det vil bli tatt nye pr\u00f8ver, sier Kvamme.", "Informasjonssjef Ellen Fl\u00f8 Skagen sier at de er orientert om at det er tatt pr\u00f8ver.", "- Funnet er under grenseverdiene for det som er tillatt. Dette er ikke et problem for mattyggheten, sier Skagen.", "Hun sier at Nortura f\u00f8lger opp saken med \u00e5 ta ekstra pr\u00f8ver en periode."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c2f5627b39e5f2da79cdcd733eb8e55441d73ecf55798d43bc1172241cf47940"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-09-21T18:47:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bakterien er funnet i kyllingkj\u00f8tt fra Nortura."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11625253.ece/y7rxso/ALTERNATES/w980-default/StOlavs06121212.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a1c7cc65b851343d65ce440fcda5892864e677ec.jpg?59162973"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Listeriabakterier funnet ved St. Olavs Hospital -adressa.no", "- Ble bekymret", "F\u00f8lger opp", "- Under grenseverdiene"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "a1c7cc65b851343d65ce440fcda5892864e677ec"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "nortura"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["funnet", "kj\u00f8kkenet"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kvinne", "kunnskapssenteret", "olavs hospital", "analysesenteret", "st. olav", "adresseavisen", "st. olavs hospital"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ellen fl\u00f8 skagen", "gunnar kvamme"]}, {"fi